# OutlineBorder

`TxOutlineBorder` border/ring/ring-offsetoverflow/clipPath/mask slot

## Basic Usage

### Basic
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="OutlineBorderBasicDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxOutlineBorder :ring-width="2" ring-color="var(--tx-color-primary)" :offset="2" offset-bg="var(--tx-bg-color)">
      <TxAvatar src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1?v=4" />
    </TxOutlineBorder>

    <TxOutlineBorder
      variant="border"
      :border-width="2"
      border-color="var(--tx-border-color)"
      :padding="2"
      shape="rect"
      :border-radius="12"
    >
      <img
        src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2?v=4"
        style="width:40px;height:40px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:12px;"
      >
    </TxOutlineBorder>
  </template>
---
:::

## Mask Clipping (Example: Hexagon)

### Mask Clip
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="OutlineBorderMaskClipDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxOutlineBorder
      variant="ring"
      :ring-width="2"
      ring-color="var(--tx-color-primary)"
      clip-mode="mask"
